# CRM repo conventions

Placeholder until the CRM app is scaffolded. Follow these defaults when adding code.

## Stack

- TypeScript, single `package.json` at repo root.
- One command serves UI + API: `npm run dev`.

## Layout (TBD at scaffold)

- API routes: `src/server/` or `app/api/`
- UI: `src/client/` or `app/`
- Shared types: colocate with API or `src/types/`

## Data

- Local persistence: SQLite or JSON file (per `docs/crm-poc-scope.md`).
- No external DB required for PoC.

## Quality

- Run `npm test` and `npm run lint` before marking work done.
- Match existing file naming and import style in the repo.
